features: LEVTEX BABY TANZANIA : A beautiful accessory for any baby nursery, the Tanzania crib fitted sheet features lion, giraffe and elephant in charcoal and tan tossed among jungle leaves. The fitted sheet fits standard crib and toddler bed mattresses. This fitted sheet is so versatile and can work with any nursery decor you may choose.

GENDER NEUTRAL BABY ACCESSORIES: The charcoal, cream and tan color palette of the Tanzania fitted sheet makes this, or any of the nursery accessories that coordinate with the Levtex Tanzania collection, the perfect baby shower gift or accent for a new nursery.

MADE WITH BABY IN MIND: At Levtex, our range of baby accessories starts with your baby's comfort in mind. Our fitted sheet is made from 100% cotton, with a reenforced elastic all around the bottom to keep it snug to your mattress. It is easy to care for, machine washable and easy to line dry or in your dryer on low.

ADORABLE JUNGLE THEME: You will think you are in the African veld with our adorable jungle animals look. This adorable fitted sheet completes your Levtex Baby Tanzania baby's room or is just a great, soft fitted sheet for you to have in your baby's nursery.

COORDINATE YOUR BABY NURSERY DECOR: The Tanzania Crib Bedding Collection fills the nursery with a friendly troupe of jungle animals. Coordinate babyÕs room with other items from the Tanzania range including the fitted sheet, changing pad cover, fuzzy blanket, mobile, a rail guard and a matching stuffed toy.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: TANZANIA COLLECTION Your little one will delight in the jungle animals in this 5 Piece Crib Bedding Set by Levtex Baby. This design is created using a myriad of fabrications, textures and fur. Designed in grey and beige, this charming set is decorated with an elephant, lion and giraffe that are appliqued and embroidered, with an embroidered border and grey binding as well as ric rac. Ther handsome, tailored bed skirt is made from a beautiful charcoal arrow print. The decal set allows you to make your own fantastic wall mural. There are many additional items that coordinate with this collection, like our stuffed toy, mobile, lamp, hamper, extra print cotton fitted sheet, change pad cover and rail guard.

Tanzania 5 piece set includes... The Tanzania set includes the fitted sheet, diaper stacker, decal, quilt and bed skirt. Tanzania Rail Guard This useful and versatile crib rail guard ties easily over the top of the long side of your crib to complete your Tanzania jungle nursery look. Tanzania Plush Toy Here is a special friend for your baby. Furry appliqued and so cute, this baby lion will be a fuzzy companion to any child.
Tanzania Plush Blanket Tanzania Fitted Sheet Tanzania mobile Tanzania Change Pad Cover Fiona Plush ADDITIONAL ITEMS AVAILABLE

About Levtex Baby Our products are thoughtfully designed in Santa Monica, CA. We combine cotton, woven fabrics, linen blends and soft textures to create an artisanal look and feel. We believe that details make the difference. Each item is designed and manufactured with the utmost care.Inspired by the fresh California sunshine, we combine our laid back lifestyle with our passion for great design. Fun textiles, great fabrics and textures are what we live for. We love classic looks infused with the contemporary and the eclectic. With cutting edge design and a commitment to quality and aesthetic, we set out to bring a fresh vision to each collection. We want your nursery to be a haven of warmth, safety and love. Our favorite nurseries are coordinated, but easy to live in; designed with a dash of the unexpected; fun and comfortable and always deeply personal, reflecting your style. MADE WITH LOVE

reviews.reviewText: I bought the entire nursery set for our little one and it is just adorable! I love that you can buy extra sheets and things to go with it so that you aren't stuck with only one. We bought this for our little girls nursery it really does work great as a unisex design.
